::Chordate::

Chordate lands near the ocean, his scanner trying to locate Riptide.

"New bot," he says into his comm-link, hoping that the new bot might have his 
on, "This is Chordate, second command of the Maximal battle cruiser The 
Cybertronian Fire. Do you read me?"
